    "name": "Cottonville",
    "steam_appid": 3290600,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从播种到缝制时尚服饰，每天都充满创意和农耕乐趣。经营你的工作室，利用缝纫图案制作独特的服装，并根据顾客的要求为他们打扮。定制你的角色，尝试不同的风格，实现你的时尚梦想。是时候通过种植获得成功了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/2a176174b7fa045b95d253e3f3321b7a.poster.avif?t=1754306561\" width=680 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/2a176174b7fa045b95d253e3f3321b7a.webm?t=1754306561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>逃离棉花镇</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >朋友出人意料地提出去 Cottonville 过新生活，这可能正是你所需要的。在这个宁静的小镇上，远离 Friglight 的喧嚣，一家小型家庭缝纫店正在等着你。科顿维尔为您提供了一个舒适的避风港，您可以在这里重新开始，一针一线地开创自己的事业，同时让大城市的喧嚣渐渐远去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/7ed2d1717300606693bb6f31a7714486.poster.avif?t=1754306561\" width=680 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/7ed2d1717300606693bb6f31a7714486.webm?t=1754306561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义角色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让你的角色真正属于你自己！选择发型、眼睛、皮肤以及更多与你的风格相匹配的服装。随着你的进步，解锁新的时尚单品，扩充你的衣橱，以反映你在棉花镇的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/6ea21c0ae87282a9a37a941a88663e21.poster.avif?t=1754306561\" width=680 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/6ea21c0ae87282a9a37a941a88663e21.webm?t=1754306561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>时尚事业从农场开始</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是种植农作物还是制作时尚服饰，科顿维尔都将农场生活的简单乐趣与时尚设计的激情完美结合。你将在农场里学到从布料制作到时装造型的所有知识！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/8f8c65927793b5e2868c52f8808242cc.poster.avif?t=1754306561\" width=680 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/8f8c65927793b5e2868c52f8808242cc.webm?t=1754306561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种植和收获棉花、亚麻和竹子等基本作物，采集鲜花制成天然染料来制作布料，所有布料都有七种不同的颜色。购买新的缝纫图案，扩大您的装扮选择范围，制作更多时尚服饰。您的农场提供制作时尚服装所需的一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/a8dd650210b9df93011a77bf841734ef.poster.avif?t=1754306561\" width=680 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/a8dd650210b9df93011a77bf841734ef.webm?t=1754306561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经营您的工作室</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的工作室是棉花镇时尚世界的核心！您可以使用一套缝纫图样集缝制、染色和定制服装，以满足客户的需求。倾听他们的要求，混合和搭配面料，创造出适合他们个性的服装。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/f4762298901784f09980bff9a6951e20.poster.avif?t=1754306561\" width=680 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/f4762298901784f09980bff9a6951e20.webm?t=1754306561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位顾客都有自己的故事，而你的设计能让他们绽放光彩。无论是节日的奇装异服，冬季的保暖毛衣，还是夏季的清凉装，您的精品店都会成为镇上的时尚中心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/2c38f3bff498226db2e2e6cdb44f0aa7.poster.avif?t=1754306561\" width=680 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290600/extras/2c38f3bff498226db2e2e6cdb44f0aa7.webm?t=1754306561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏内容包括</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可收集 60 多种不同颜色的图案（共 120 多种）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 种发色供选择 15 种独特的发型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >眉毛、睫毛、眼睛、嘴巴和皮肤颜色--我们都为您准备好了！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 种可制作的作物，有 7 种颜色可在您的锯木机中混合使用</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 多个小时充满时尚气息的农耕和故事！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
